The paper describes a neural question answering system for biomedical QA, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. The most relevant arXiv CS sub-category is likely to be cs.CL (Computation and Language), which covers topics such as natural language processing, information retrieval, and text mining. Other possible sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), which are all relevant to the paper's methodology and approach.
